description:

a DEFESA dele.
name: ELÁSTICO
note:
<is Toy>
<IconIndex:69>

<follow action>
 if target.isStateAffected(99) 
   add state 100: target
   remove state 99: target
 else if target.isStateAffected(98) 
   add state 99: target
   remove state 98: target
 else 
   add state 98: target
end

animation 219: target

eval: BattleManager._logWindow.push("addText", target.name() + " perdeu DEFESA.")
else
eval: Gamefall.OmoriFixes.parseNoStateChange(target.name(), 'DEFESA', "baixa!")
end
</follow action>
<AntiFail>

description:

note:
<Remove State Category: EMOTION>
<is Toy>
<IconIndex:70>
<AntiFail>

<Enemy or Actor Select>

<target action>
SE: BA_calm_down, 90, 100, 0
wait: 25
if target.isAnyEmotionAffected(true)
eval: BattleManager.addText(target.name() + " se sente NEUTRO.")
else
eval: BattleManager.addText("Não teve efeito.")
end

evaL: target.removeStateCategoryAll("SAD")

</target action>

description:

note:
<IconIndex:15>

<damage formula>
if(!$gameParty.inBattle()) {
AudioManager.playSe({name:"BA_life_jam_1",volume:100,pitch:100, pan:0})
}
if(target.isStateAffected(198))
value = b.mhp
else
value = b.mhp * .5
</damage formula>

<target action>
eval: $gameTemp._noTarget = !target
action animation
wait for animation
action effect
wait for effect
</target action>

<follow action>
if $gameTemp._noTarget
eval: SceneManager._scene._logWindow.push("addText", "It had no effect.")
eval: SceneManager._scene._logWindow.push("waitForNewLine")
eval: $gameTemp._noTarget = undefined
end
</follow action>
